name: Empire_Deco-Style_Bamboo_Folding_Chairs
description:
These Empire Deco-Style Folding Chairs feature a high quality bamboo wood construction, with a clear coated glossy finish, curved back and supportive braces provide extra comfort and support, folds easily.
This versatile chair can be used in your dining room, or for weddings and other upscale events, can also be used in your patio or by the pool.
This beautiful chair will highlight your indoor or outdoor event without the need for chair covers or bows.
